OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely sunny and dry and
OL,6,Fbecoming widely very warm or hot
OL,7,Finland, away from cooler and breezier
OL,8,Fcoastal areas. A few, localised
OL,9,Fshowers or thunderstorms are possible
OL,10,Fat times, mainly across Norfolk until
OL,11,Faround midday and elsewhere by late
OL,12,Fafternoon.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FAny showers or thunderstorms
OL,15,Feasing and skies clearing to leave a
OL,16,Ffine, dry night. Rather warm for many
OL,17,Feastern areas, although feeling
OL,18,Fslightly fresher in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
