OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSome sunshine likely, although
OL,6,Fprobably largely cloudy through the
OL,7,Fmiddle of the day with a risk of
OL,8,Fshowers, perhaps thundery. Slightly
OL,9,Fcooler for many areas, but still
OL,10,Fgenerally very warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry,
OL,13,Flargely sunny and very warm, locally
OL,14,Fhot on Saturday. Trending cooler and
OL,15,Fmore changeable from Sunday. An
OL,16,Fincreased chance of rain, but still
OL,17,Fsome fine, warm weather at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
